{"ID":270295, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"295\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs294.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs296.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 295<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">When I heard of the death of our beloved Brother Barnes, it would not have affected me so\n  much, if I had the opportunity of burying him in the land of Zion.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I believe those who have buried their friends here, their condition is enviable. Look at Jacob and\n  Joseph in Egypt, how they required their friends to bury them in the tomb of their fathers.<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> See the\n  expense which attended the embalming and the going up of the great company to the burial.<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">It has always been considered a great calamity not to obtain an honorable burial: and one of the\n  greatest curses the ancient prophets could put on any man, was that he should go without a burial.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I have said, Father, I desire to die here among the Saints. But if this is not Thy will, and I go\n  hence and die,<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> wilt Thou find some kind friend to bring my body back,<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> and gather my friends who\n  have fallen in foreign lands, and bring them up hither, that we may all lie together.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I will tell you what I want. If tomorrow I shall be called to lie in yonder tomb, in the morning\n  of the resurrection let me strike hands<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> with my father, and cry, &ldquo;My father,&rdquo; and he will say, &ldquo;My\n  son, my son,&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> as soon as the rock rends<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> and before we come out of our graves.<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">And may we contemplate these thing so? Yes, if we learn how to live and how to die. When we\n  lie down we contemplate how we may rise in the morning; and it is pleasing for friends to lie down\n  together, locked in the arms of love,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> to sleep and wake in each other&rsquo;s embrace and renew their\n  conversation.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Righteous to Have Joy in the Resurrection <\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Would you think it strange if I relate what I have seen in vision in relation to this interesting\n  theme? Those who have died in Jesus Christ<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> may expect to enter into all that fruition of joy when\n  they come forth,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> which they possessed or anticipated here.<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">So plain was the vision, that I actually saw men, before they had ascended from the tomb, as\n  though they were getting up slowly. They took each other by the hand and said to each other, &ldquo;My\n  father, my son, my mother, my daughter, my brother, my sister.&rdquo;  And when the voice calls for the\n  dead to arise,<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> suppose I am laid by the side of my father, what would be the first joy of my heart?\n  To meet my father, my mother,<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106084\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106084)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106084)\">Gen. 50:7,25-26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106138\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106138)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106138)\">Ex. 13:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106368\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106368)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106368)\">Josh. 24:32<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109020\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109020)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109020)\">Acts 7:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106083\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106083)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106083)\">Gen. 50:7-9,14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106709\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106709)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106709)\">Ps. 39:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106086\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106086)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106086)\">Gen. 50:25<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106139\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106139)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106139)\">Ex. 13:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106369\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106369)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106369)\">Josh. 24:32<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109021\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109021)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109021)\">Acts 7:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106597\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106597)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106597)\">Job 17:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106955\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106955)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106955)\">Prov. 22:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106415\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106415)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106415)\">2 Sam. 18:33<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106416\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106416)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106416)\">2 Sam. 19:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117026\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117026)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117026)\">Abr. 3:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112584\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112584)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112584)\">3 Ne. 10:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108282\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108282)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108282)\">Matt. 27:52-53<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112510\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112510)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112510)\">Hel. 14:25<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112682\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112682)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112682)\">3 Ne. 23:9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116498\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116498)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116498)\">D&amp;C 133:56<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111077\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111077)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111077)\">2 Ne. 1:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113151\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113151)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113151)\">D&amp;C 6:20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113522\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113522)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113522)\">D&amp;C 29:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108680\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108680)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108680)\">John 5:28-29<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112351\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112351)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112351)\">Alma 46:39,41<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112820\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112820)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112820)\">Morm. 9:13-14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114510\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114510)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114510)\">D&amp;C 76:118<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108681\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108681)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108681)\">John 5:28-29<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109943\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109943)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109943)\">1 Thes. 4:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114403\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114403)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114403)\">D&amp;C 76:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}